convidá-la para sair?

326
00:21:18,235 --> 00:21:20,078
Sim.

327
00:21:20,529 --> 00:21:21,826
Talvez.

328
00:21:22,823 --> 00:21:24,666
Certo.

329
00:21:29,413 --> 00:21:31,882
Talvez eu convide.

330
00:21:35,836 --> 00:21:37,964
- Boa noite.
